OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782402488
OL,3,CTicket fraudster 'preyed on' Taylor
OL,4,CSwift fans to defraud more than #5,000
OL,6,FA ticket fraudster who swindled more
OL,7,Fthan #5,000 by "preying on"
OL,8,Funsuspecting Taylor Swift fans has
OL,9,Favoided jail.
OL,11,FJordan Moore created posts on Facebook
OL,12,Fand Gumtree claiming to be selling two
OL,13,Ftickets to the popstar's concert in
OL,14,FDublin after his relationship broke
OL,15,Fdown.
OL,17,FHe defrauded seven victims between
OL,18,FNovember 2023 and March 2025, Chester
OL,19,FCrown Court was told.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
