FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782402488
OL,3,CTicket fraudster 'preyed on' Taylor
OL,4,CSwift fans to defraud more than #5,000
OL,6,FMore, 32, of Little Sutton, Ellesmere
OL,7,FPort, was handed a 19-month prison
OL,8,Fsentence, suspended for two years,
OL,9,Fafter pleading guilty to seven counts
OL,10,Fof fraud by false representation.
OL,12,FHe was also ordered to complete 100
OL,13,Fhours of unpaid work and must pay
OL,14,F#3,808 in compensation.
OL,16,FTwo charges related to the fraudulent
OL,17,Fsale of greyhound equipment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
