FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782402488
OL,3,CTicket fraudster 'preyed on' Taylor
OL,4,CSwift fans to defraud more than #5,000
OL,6,FSpeaking after the sentencing, PC
OL,7,FHindley, from Cheshire Police, said:
OL,8,F"Moore preyed on his victims,
OL,9,Fspecifically using Taylor Swift
OL,10,Ftickets as a hook to lure them in and
OL,11,Fdefraud them of thousands of pounds.
OL,13,F"He was well aware that what he was
OL,14,Fdoing was wrong, but he thought that
OL,15,Fhe would be able to outsmart his
OL,16,Fvictims and avoid justice.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
