OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782402488
OL,3,CTicket fraudster 'preyed on' Taylor
OL,4,CSwift fans to defraud more than #5,000
OL,6,F"Unfortunately for him, thanks to the
OL,7,Finformation provided by the victims,
OL,8,Fand the evidence gathered by the team
OL,9,Fhere at Cheshire Police, his plans
OL,10,Ffell apart and he has now been held
OL,11,Faccountable for his actions."
OL,13,FFollowing the court's decision on 19
OL,14,FJune, police issued a warning to the
OL,15,Fpublic about the hidden dangers of
OL,16,Fpurchasing tickets via social media
OL,17,Faccounts.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
