OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782402488
OL,3,CTicket fraudster 'preyed on' Taylor
OL,4,CSwift fans to defraud more than #5,000
OL,6,FOfficers noted that while online
OL,7,Fplatforms make buying and selling
OL,8,Fitems much easier, they also make it
OL,9,Feasier for dishonest sellers to
OL,10,Fexploit victims.
OL,12,FVictims can report fraud by calling
OL,13,FReport Fraud on 0300 123 2040 or by
OL,14,Fvisiting the official Report Fraud
OL,15,Fwebsite.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
